Class ScoreData

java.lang.Object
  ScoreData
All Implemented Interfaces:
Comparable<ScoreData>
public class ScoreData
extends Object
implements Comparable<ScoreData>

This class will create a class that holds the user name and the score achieved in it. It implements Comparable so that it can be compared based on scores in a PriorityQueue

modified with help from: http://onjava.com/onjava/2003/03/12/java_comp.html
